HEADWORD: officialdom
<hw>officialdom</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The body of all people elected
or appointed to administer a government, taken collectively.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> government officials.</syn>⟦br⟧
